# Pink Cushion Cut Diamond: Lab or Natural — What Every Buyer Should Know

A pink cushion cut diamond exists in two completely different universes depending on whether you're buying natural or lab-grown. Natural fancy pink cushion cut diamonds start at [$9,488 for a GIA 1ct Fancy Brownish Pink SI2](https://www.bluenile.com/colored-diamond-details/pink-28204124?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational) — and climb to [$979,347 for a 1.02ct Fancy Intense Purplish Pink](https://www.bluenile.com/colored-diamond-details/pink-21749730?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational). Lab-grown flips the equation: a [5ct IGI Fancy Vivid Pink VS1 starts at $3,045](https://www.bluenile.com/colored-diamond-details/pink-29194960?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational).

The difference is not just price. It's the entire category of buyer this stone is for.

---

**TL;DR**

For almost every retail buyer, lab-grown pink cushion cut is the answer. Natural fancy pink cushion cuts — with pure GIA "Fancy Pink" or "Fancy Intense Pink" grading — are auction-house territory. Here's where the money actually lands:

- **Lab best value:** [5ct IGI Fancy Vivid Pink VS1 — $3,045](https://www.bluenile.com/colored-diamond-details/pink-29194960?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational). Five carats of vivid pink for under $4,000. Nothing in natural even comes close.
- **Natural entry point:** [1.02ct GIA Fancy Brownish Pink SI2 — $9,488](https://www.bluenile.com/colored-diamond-details/pink-28204124?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational). The "brown" modifier means more brown than pink to the eye — be aware of that trade-off.
- **True natural pink (no modifier):** [1ct GIA Fancy Brown Pink VS2 — $38,006](https://www.bluenile.com/colored-diamond-details/pink-20891251?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational). This is a pure pink stone, not an approximation.

→ **Priority rule:** The cushion cut is the best shape for pink diamonds — The Colour Cut Advantage means it pools color saturation better than any other cut. Whatever you buy, cushion is the right shape choice.

